org.janelia.flyem.neuprinter.model

Class Neuron

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.janelia.flyem.neuprinter.model.Neuron

  • public class Neuron
extends java.lang.Object
    A class representing a neuron, as read from a neuron JSON file. Each neuron has an id, size, name, and status, but no synapse information. (cf. the BodyWithSynapses class that represents bodies with synapses)
